What we took and what we changed
--------------------------------
TAKEN (structure / pattern only):
  - The skill shape: Overview + applicable-contexts keyword line + a "brand
    guidelines" block carrying the brand's specific assets + a "features"/how-to
    application section + technical/integration details.
  - The convention of a `license:` field in the SKILL.md frontmatter.

CHANGED (100% original content — none of Anthropic's brand content is reproduced):
  - The upstream skill applies Anthropic's OWN visual brand (colors #141413 /
    #d97757 etc., Poppins/Lora typography, pptx styling). NONE of that content is
    copied here.
  - This skill applies a per-ARTIST textual VOICE: positioning, personas,
    messaging pillars, approved claims, do/do-not lexicon, and on-voice example
    captions, loaded from the per-tenant pack + the winning-strategies KB.
  - All substance is original and grounded in docs/skills/winning-strategies-kb.md.

